      • TypeB

        public TypeB​(java.lang.String scenario,
             java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> lista,
             int n)
      throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Main constructor for TypeB. For generation purposes it uses the scenario given as a parameter to create a DataExtractor and with that obtain the seed used for the random selection in the parent class. Given the percentual value, it saves it as an absolute value so the parent class only uses that to make the selection.
        Parameters:
        scenario - chosen scenario for the DataExtractor
        lista - list to do the random selection on
        n - percentual value of desired outputs
        Throws:
        java.lang.InterruptedException

      • TypeB

        public TypeB​(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> lista,
             int n,
             DataExtractor de)
      throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Verification constructor for TypeB. Same function as main constructor, but it receives a DataExtractor that will be used to obtain the seed.
        Parameters:
        lista - list to do the random selection on
        n - percentual value of desired outputs
        de - already generated DataExtractor for seed purposes
        Throws:
        java.lang.InterruptedException
